import React from "react";
import {
  BlockContentDiscription,
  BlockContentFooter,
  BlockContentOur,
  BlockLOGOFooter,
  BlockTitleOur,
  ConatainerContentFooter,
  ContainerFooter,
  ContentOurFooter,
} from "./style";
import LOGO from "../Logo/logoFooter/index";

import { FaMailBulk, FaPhoneAlt, FaSearchLocation } from "react-icons/fa";

function Index() {
  return (
    <>
      <ContainerFooter>
        <ConatainerContentFooter>
          <BlockContentFooter>
            <BlockLOGOFooter>
              <LOGO />
            </BlockLOGOFooter>
            <BlockContentDiscription margin size>
              ShopeTeam - ứng dụng mua sắm trực tuyến thú vị, tin cậy, an toàn
              và miễn phí!
            </BlockContentDiscription>
            <BlockContentDiscription white>
              <FaMailBulk style={{ paddingRight: "20px" }} /> shopteam@gmail.com
            </BlockContentDiscription>
            <BlockContentDiscription white>
              <FaPhoneAlt style={{ paddingRight: "20px" }} />
              082 875 84 **
            </BlockContentDiscription>
            <BlockContentDiscription white>
              <FaSearchLocation style={{ paddingRight: "20px" }} /> 06 Tran Van
              On, Phu Hoa, Thu Dau Mot, Binh Duong
            </BlockContentDiscription>
          </BlockContentFooter>
          <BlockContentFooter>
            <BlockTitleOur>Our Recent Posts</BlockTitleOur>
            <BlockContentOur>
              <ContentOurFooter>
                Visit Thailand, Bali And China
              </ContentOurFooter>
              <ContentOurFooter white>September 7, 2016</ContentOurFooter>
            </BlockContentOur>
            <BlockContentOur>
              <ContentOurFooter>The Sound Of Our Jungle</ContentOurFooter>
              <ContentOurFooter white>September 7, 2016</ContentOurFooter>
            </BlockContentOur>
            <BlockContentOur>
              <ContentOurFooter>
                Visit Thailand, Bali And China
              </ContentOurFooter>
              <ContentOurFooter white>September 7, 2016</ContentOurFooter>
            </BlockContentOur>
            <BlockContentOur>
              <ContentOurFooter>The Sound Of Our Jungle</ContentOurFooter>
              <ContentOurFooter white>September 7, 2016</ContentOurFooter>
            </BlockContentOur>
          </BlockContentFooter>
          <BlockContentFooter>
            <BlockTitleOur>Our Recent Posts</BlockTitleOur>
            <ContentOurFooter>The Sound Of Our Jungle</ContentOurFooter>
          </BlockContentFooter>
          <BlockContentFooter>
            Our Instagram Aliquam lorem ante, dapibus inviver raqui feugiat a,
            tellus. Phasellus null
          </BlockContentFooter>
        </ConatainerContentFooter>
      </ContainerFooter>
    </>
  );
}

export default Index;
